To VIM working, we need to:

Install these VIM plugins:
1) Perforce    http://www.vim.org//script.php?script_id=240
2) NerdTree    https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree    

Install these syntax files:
1) verilog_systemverilog.vim    http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1586

Install these fonts (for GUI):
1) Inconsolata\ for\ Powerline\ 11
